---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab: Get to Know the Founders - parcelLab"
  description="Meet the three founders of parcelLab -- Anton Eder, Julian Krenge, and Tobias Buxhoidt -- and learn about their backgrounds and vision."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab -- Get to Know the Founders</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2019-10-24">October 24, 2019</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          More than 350 online retailers across Europe and the USA, including roughly one-third of Germany's top 100 e-commerce companies, depend on parcelLab's services. Notable customers include Lidl, IKEA, and MediaMarktSaturn. The company employs approximately 50 post-purchase communication specialists with offices in Munich, London, and Paris.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Three entrepreneurs -- Anton, Julian, and Tobias -- established parcelLab in 2015 with a shared mission to enhance the post-purchase shopping experience.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Anton Eder -- Chief Operating Officer</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Munich's University of Applied Sciences & Stockholm's Royal Institute of Technology</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Anton manages marketing and organizational operations while overseeing customer success across international markets. Previously held marketing positions at Adconion Media Group, IDG Tech Media, and Spiceworks.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"We identify critical delivery events through real-time monitoring and deliver personalized communications via email, SMS, Facebook, or merchant apps to strengthen loyalty and drive upselling."</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Julian Krenge -- Chief Technology Officer</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Computer Science, RWTH Aachen University</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Julian develops and continuously improves the product while ensuring retailer support quality. His focus is on building technology that makes the post-purchase experience seamless for both brands and their customers.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Online retail competition intensifies daily. Customer experience differentiates winners. Companies must prioritize customer focus for sustainable success."</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Tobias Buxhoidt -- Chief Executive Officer</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">University of Karlsruhe & University of Newcastle | Industrial Engineering</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Tobias ensures every retailer receives optimal customer experience solutions. Previously worked as a development engineer at BMW Group and management consultant at Barkawi Management Consulting.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Relentless focus on customer value matters most. Top companies like Apple, Amazon, and ASOS exemplify this dedication."</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Together, Anton, Julian, and Tobias bring complementary skills in operations, technology, and business strategy to parcelLab -- united by a shared belief that the post-purchase experience is where lasting customer relationships are built.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
